  "title": "Redstone Jukeboxes",
  "description": "A mod for minecraft that tweaks vanilla jukebox functions. Includes basic redstone jukebox, repeating jukebox and tiered advanced jukeboxes with inventories.",
  "body": "![MC version](https://img.shields.io/badge/for_MC-1.20.1,_1.20.2-orange) \n[![Discord invite](https://img.shields.io/discord/1279772493783105536?style=flat-square&label=%20&logo=discord&color=2D2D2D)](https://discord.gg/kT6r9TVmnx) \n[![YouTube](https://img.shields.io/youtube/channel/subscribers/UCtcAtfWvYraGKLLVlItOuoA?style=flat-square&label=%20&logo=youtube&logoColor=ff2129&color=2d2d2d)](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtcAtfWvYraGKLLVlItOuoA) \n[![GitHub](https://img.shields.io/badge/-GitHub-2d2d2d?style=flat-square&logo=GitHub&logoColor=white)](https://github.com/Tau-ri-Dev/Mod-RS-Jukeboxes) \n[![Just Stargate Mod](https://img.shields.io/badge/-JustStargateMod-2d2d2d?style=flat-square&logo=Pinboard&logoColor=3c85e6)](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jsg)\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/955/929/banner-logo.png\" alt=\"Logo\" width=\"1000\" height=\"560\" style=\"display:block\"/>\n\n \n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <td> \n      <p><img width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"https://vzge.me/bust/700/171b6e4003d641feac5aa31658de6832.png\"></p> \n    </td>\n    <td></td>\n    <td>\n      <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:left\">Finally, it's here... You no longer need to search for jukeboxes controlled by a redstone signal! A simple mod that has finally answered the long-standing call so many people have made. We have answered this call and expanded the basic idea. And now, the most important thing: Redstone Jukeboxes are compatible with mods that add custom music discs!</p></strong>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n\n\n\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <td>\n      <strong><p style=\"font-family:monospace;text-align:left\">We present to you several types of new jukeboxes controlled by redstone signals. From a simple jukebox – which you activate only with a redstone signal, to a repeating jukebox that loops a track, to advanced jukeboxes that can hold multiple discs! For more mods and info join our Discord community!</p></strong>\n    </td>\n    <td></td>\n    <td> \n      <p><img width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"https://vzge.me/bust/700/b9889cd78c4d4b3385bd2c1415363f17.png?y=-40\"></p> \n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/956/70/support.png\" alt=\"Support us title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"118\" style=\"display:block\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=TAN5E9QXQE2SS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n  <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/956/53/pp.png\" width=\"1000\">\n</a>\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n\n\n\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/955/959/otherprojects.png\" alt=\"Other projects title\" width=\"1000\" height=\"118\" style=\"display:block\"/>\n&nbsp;\n<table style=\"width:100%\">\n  <tr>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jsg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/1039/875/638565645126910597.png\"></p>\n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/customization/jsg-addon-mwpoo\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/910/426/638364466607972492.png\"></p> \n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/jsg-sd\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/906/937/638357491075995069.png\"></p> \n      </a>\n    </th>\n    <th> \n      <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/secretsofavalon\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n        <p><img width=\"150\